{"tid":979313,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[業餘]想照住幅圖黎畫(2)","createTime":"2019-01-12T15:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T12:46:20.000Z","uid":92951,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3c724f8fc7a72d505d4a57fa5161b2f1536e84","tid":979313,"uid":92951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"上回提要:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/782174/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/782174/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cQypai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cQypai.png&h=e42bf175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VLeS3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VLeS3G.jpg&h=c44416ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次畫左幾日 夾埋23個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次要畫既係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDYstCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDYstCc.png&h=16391a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n難度又幾級跳  <br />\n希望唔會爛尾 順便開個POST督促自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有鑑於見到隔離post填色比賽神童才華洋溢<br />\n幾歲人仔油顏色咁撚靚<br />\n雖然我油顏色小學雞都不如 <br />\n特登拎番盒生埋麈既顏色筆出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有預感今次會挑戰失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7793ba10b78fd6541ec8da9e1047f6eb493a0e3a","tid":979313,"uid":92951,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPa6KcU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPa6KcU.jpg&